        },
        "innerText": "pādakārammaṇena"
      },
      " catutthajjhānassa paṭibhāganimittasaṅkhātena ārammaṇena phuṭṭhe okāse gate pavatte pana sadde suṇāti. Dibbasotañāṇaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "1067-8.Eso adhigatābhiñño yogī pādakārammaṇena catutthajjhānassa paṭibhāganimittasaṅkhātena ārammaṇena phuṭṭhe okāse gate pavatte pana sadde suṇāti. Dibbasotañāṇaṃ."
  },
  {
