        },
        "innerText": "1075"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kāmāvacaracittañcāti"
      },
      " kāmāvacarasattānaṃ kāmāvacaracittañca. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rūpārūpesu"
      },
      " rūpabhavārūpabhavesu sattānaṃ mānasañca. Kiṃ bhūtaṃ? Sarāgādippabhedakaṃ mānasaṃ sabbaṃ cetopariyañāṇaṃ jānāti. Cetopariyañāṇaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "1075.Kāmāvacaracittañcāti kāmāvacarasattānaṃ kāmāvacaracittañca. Rūpārūpesu rūpabhavārūpabhavesu sattānaṃ mānasañca. Kiṃ bhūtaṃ? Sarāgādippabhedakaṃ mānasaṃ sabbaṃ cetopariyañāṇaṃ jānāti. Cetopariyañāṇaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "1077-82"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Nisajjā sabbapacchimā"
      },
      "ti sabbesaṃ iriyāpathānaṃ pacchā jātā nisajjā bhikkhunā āvajjitabbā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tato pabhuti"
      },
      " tato sabbapacchimato nisajjāto pabhuti taṃ sabbaṃ pacchimanisajjaṃ ādiṃ katvā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "paṭilomakkamā"
      },
      " paṭilomakkamena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sabbaṃ"
      },
      " attanā kataṃ āvajjitabbaṃ. Asmiṃ bhave ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yāva"
      },
      " yattakaṃ kālaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sandhi"
      },
      " paṭisandhi hoti, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tāva"
      },
      " tattakaṃ kālaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kataṃ"
      },
      " kiriyaṃ tena bhikkhunā āvajjitabbaṃ. Purimasmiṃ bhavepi cutikkhaṇepi nibbattaṃ nāmarūpañca sādhukaṃ āvajjitabbaṃ. Cutikkhaṇe nibbatte tasmiṃ nāmarūpe evaṃ bhikkhunā āvajjitabbe yadā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tadeva"
      },
      " tameva nāmarūpaṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā cutikkhaṇe manodvāre ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "manakkāro"
      },
      " manodvārāvajjanacittaṃ uppajjati. Pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "1077-82.Nisajjā sabbapacchimāti sabbesaṃ iriyāpathānaṃ pacchā jātā nisajjā bhikkhunā āvajjitabbā. Tato pabhuti tato sabbapacchimato nisajjāto pabhuti taṃ sabbaṃ pacchimanisajjaṃ ādiṃ katvā paṭilomakkamā paṭilomakkamena sabbaṃ attanā kataṃ āvajjitabbaṃ. Asmiṃ bhave yāva yattakaṃ kālaṃ sandhi paṭisandhi hoti, tāva tattakaṃ kālaṃ kataṃ kiriyaṃ tena bhikkhunā āvajjitabbaṃ. Purimasmiṃ bhavepi cutikkhaṇepi nibbattaṃ nāmarūpañca sādhukaṃ āvajjitabbaṃ. Cutikkhaṇe nibbatte tasmiṃ nāmarūpe evaṃ bhikkhunā āvajjitabbe yadā tadeva tameva nāmarūpaṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā cutikkhaṇe manodvāre manakkāro manodvārāvajjanacittaṃ uppajjati. Pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "1086-96"
      },
      ". Abhiññāpādakaṃ kasiṇārammaṇaṃ jhānaṃ abhinīhārakkhamaṃ katvā imesu tīsu kasiṇesu katapuññehi. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tasmā tamitaraṃ vāpī"
      },
      "ti ālokakasiṇaṃ vā itaraṃ vāpi kasiṇadvayaṃ yathākkamaṃ ",
      " uppādetvā upacārabhūmiyaṃyeva ṭhatvā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "taṃ"
      },
      " ālokakasiṇaṃ ṭhapetabbaṃ. Appanaṃ paṇḍito na uppādeyya, sace uppādeti, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "taṃ"
      },
      " ālokakasiṇaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "pādakajjhānanissitaṃ"
      },
      " pādakajjhānassa ārammaṇaṃ hoti. Vaḍḍhitassa jhānassa antogadhaṃ rūpaṃ tena yoginā passitabbaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "bhave"
      },
      " bhaveyya. Taṃ rūpaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "passato"
      },
      " passantassa ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tassa"
      },
      " yogino parikammassa vāro atikkamati, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tāvade"
      },
      " tasmiṃyeva khaṇe ālokopi ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tassa"
      },
      " yogino ālokopi khippaṃ antaradhāyati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tasmiṃ"
      },
      " āloke antarahite ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "rūpagataṃ"
      },
      " rūpaṃ na dissati. Divasampi nisīditvā passato rūpadassanaṃ hoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "1086-96. Abhiññāpādakaṃ kasiṇārammaṇaṃ jhānaṃ abhinīhārakkhamaṃ katvā imesu tīsu kasiṇesu katapuññehi. Tasmā tamitaraṃ vāpīti ālokakasiṇaṃ vā itaraṃ vāpi kasiṇadvayaṃ yathākkamaṃ uppādetvā upacārabhūmiyaṃyeva ṭhatvā taṃ ālokakasiṇaṃ ṭhapetabbaṃ. Appanaṃ paṇḍito na uppādeyya, sace uppādeti, taṃ ālokakasiṇaṃ pādakajjhānanissitaṃ pādakajjhānassa ārammaṇaṃ hoti. Vaḍḍhitassa jhānassa antogadhaṃ rūpaṃ tena yoginā passitabbaṃ bhave bhaveyya. Taṃ rūpaṃ passato passantassa tassa yogino parikammassa vāro atikkamati, tāvade tasmiṃyeva khaṇe ālokopi tassa yogino ālokopi khippaṃ antaradhāyati. Tasmiṃ āloke antarahite rūpagataṃ rūpaṃ na dissati. Divasampi nisīditvā passato rūpadassanaṃ hoti."
  },
  {
