        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Taṃcittasaṃyuta"
      },
      "nti tena catutthajjhānena yuttaṃ cittaṃ. Anāgataṃsañāṇassa parikammaṃ, yathākammūpagassa ñāṇassa ca parikammaṃ. Dibbacakkhuñāṇaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "1100-1.Taṃcittasaṃyutanti tena catutthajjhānena yuttaṃ cittaṃ. Anāgataṃsañāṇassa parikammaṃ, yathākammūpagassa ñāṇassa ca parikammaṃ. Dibbacakkhuñāṇaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "1103"
      },
      ". Yo bhikkhu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "idha"
      },
      " imasmiṃ sāsane imaṃ pana ganthaṃ suṇāti, citte karoti ca, so bhikkhu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "anena tarena"
      },
      " iminā ganthena taritvā abhidhammamahaṇṇavapāraṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yāti"
      },
      " pāpuṇāti, jānātīti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "1103. Yo bhikkhu idha imasmiṃ sāsane imaṃ pana ganthaṃ suṇāti, citte karoti ca, so bhikkhu anena tarena iminā ganthena taritvā abhidhammamahaṇṇavapāraṃ yāti pāpuṇāti, jānātīti attho."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Iti abhidhammāvatāraṭīkāya"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Abhiññāniddesavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Soḷasamo paricchedo."
  }
